      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in style! This car is in good condition and has been well-cared for, offering a smooth and dependable ride that you can truly count on. It's the perfect blend of comfort and reliability, ready to take you on your next adventure with confidence!",
      "price": 33500.0,
